
=Discussion=

"Our vision is to transform the linear fashion economy into a circular fashion system. This vision includes circular materials, design and production for circularity, cascading use of products, circular business models, as well as material recovery systems.

We want to create a movement towards a Circular Textile Economy and collaboratively work on this!

We are looking for partners, collaborations, clients, sponsors, members, researchers, makers and all people who want to support this movement and run projects together!"
(http://community.oscedays.org/t/public-wiki-vision-of-the-circular-textile-group/805)

